        <div class="main review-item" id="1312317">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2260543/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u2260543-1.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2260543/" class="name">魔球</a>

            <span class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>

        <span content="2008-02-25" class="main-meta">2008-02-25 14:29:15</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1312317/">故弄玄虚</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1312317_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1312317">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        非常故弄玄虚。本来还不算太烂，但是这个广告和百度吧那里实在吹的太好了，所以怀着兴奋的心情去看的。OMG，实在对不起我们这样对悬疑推理小说爱好者。情节实在比较无聊，还故意写的很大，号称是跨越5000年的爱恋，有么？有轰轰烈烈么？那个所谓的大秘密，一点也不吸引人。如果...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1312317-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1312317_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1312317_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1312317" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1312317">
